  "texts": [
    "We focus on binary classification tasks in this study.",
    "First, let us introduce a few concepts.",
    "For every binary prediction/classification task, the result could fall into four different categories:",
    "• true positives (TP), positive cases correctly predicted as positive;",
    "• false negatives (FN), positive cases incorrectly predicted as negative;"
  ],
